<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 3749/86 of 9 December 1986 determining the operative event for calculating levies and refunds in the rice sector </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 3749/86, millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks riisisektori maksude ja toetuste arvutamise rakendusjuht 9. detsember 1986 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1676/85 of 11 June 1985 on the value of the unit of account and the conversion rates to be applied for the purposes of the common agricultural policy (1), and in particular Article 5 (3) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 11. juuni 1985. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1676/85 &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika raames kohaldatava arvestus&uuml;hiku v&auml;&auml;rtuse ja &uuml;mberarvestuskursside kohta, (1) eriti selle artikli 5 l&otilde;iget 3, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in accordance with Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3294/86 (2), the conversion rate is to be determined using a monetary coefficient which is calculated and applied in a way similar to the way the monetary compensatory amounts are calculated; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: vastavalt komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusele (EM&Uuml;) nr 3294/86 (2) tuleb &uuml;mberarvestuskurss kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata, kasutades valuutakoefitsienti, mida arvutatakse ja kohaldatakse nagu kursikompensatsioone; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in accordance with Article 4 of Regulation (EEC) No 1676/85, if an agricultural conversion rate is altered, the alteration is to apply to the amounts in respect of which the operative event occurs after the alteration has taken effect; whereas, in accordance with Article 5 (1) (a) of that Regulation, 'operative event' means, as regards the amounts charged or granted in trade, the completion of customs import or export formalities; </inglise>
<eesti> vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1676/85 artiklile 4 kohaldatakse p&otilde;llumajandusliku &uuml;mberarvestuskursi muutmisel muudatust summade suhtes, mille puhul rakendusjuht on p&auml;rast muudatuse j&otilde;ustumist; vastavalt k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 1 punktile a k&auml;sitatakse kaubanduses makstavate v&otilde;i saadavate summade rakendusjuhuna impordi v&otilde;i ekspordiga seotud formaalsuste t&auml;itmist; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, as a result, amounts of levies and refunds fixed in advance may vary in national currency; whereas the advance fixing of levies and refunds therefore constitutes an risk for operators; whereas, as a consequence, the operative event should be defined as the date of acceptance of the application for the advance fixing of levies or refunds for the purposes of applying the conversion rate for calculating those amounts in national currency; </inglise>
<eesti> selle tulemusena v&otilde;ivad eelnevalt kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud maksude ja toetuste summad erineda omav&auml;&auml;ringust s&otilde;ltuvalt; maksude ja toetuste eelneva kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramisega kaasneb risk ettev&otilde;tjate jaoks; seet&otilde;ttu tuleks maksude v&otilde;i toetuste eelneva kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramise taotluse vastuv&otilde;tmise kuup&auml;ev m&auml;&auml;ratleda k&otilde;nealuste summade omav&auml;&auml;ringusse &uuml;mberarvestamisel kohaldatava &uuml;mberarvestuskursi rakendusjuhuna; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Cereals, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las teraviljaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The operative event for the conversion into national currency of the amounts of levies and refunds applicable in the rice sector shall be: </inglise>
<eesti> Riisisektoris kohaldatavate maksude ja toetuste summade omav&auml;&auml;ringusse &uuml;mberarvestamise rakendusjuht on: </eesti>
<inglise> - in the case of advance fixing of those amounts, the day on which the application for advance fixing is lodged, </inglise>
<eesti> - k&otilde;nealuste summade eelneva kinnitamise korral p&auml;ev, mil eelkinnitustaotlus on esitatud, </eesti>
<inglise> - in the case of advance fixing by tendering procedure, the closing date for the submission of tenders. </inglise>
<eesti> - eelneva kinnitamise korral pakkumismenetluse teel pakkumiste esitamise t&auml;htp&auml;ev. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 9 December 1986. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 9. detsember 1986 </eesti>
